What's wrong with being single!!!

Arcane Soldier: Now it's time those damn couples experience my wrath! Today shall be the day of my vengeance! Behold my power!!!
Arcane Soldier: I'm not done yet. I can still go on!

Housemaid: Whew, now I have to clean that side...

Housemaid: Look at all the mess you made! I know it feels terrible to have to work on your birthday, but you can't just go nuts and trash the place!
Arcane Soldier: You... you remembered my birthday!?
Housemaid: You've been complaining about it nonstop to other people. Of course I'd remember!
Housemaid: I know you're holding a grudge, so here's a present. I originally planned to give it to you after you got off work, but I guess giving it now can't hurt~
